  lines:
  - text: 'Welcome back Detective!


      Congrats for finishing your first challenge.'
    mood: 0
  - text: 'But let''s not celebrate to early.

'
    mood: 3
  - text: 'The hacker has moved

      to the office floor

      and inserted fake
      data!'
    mood: 4
  - text: 'Search the office,

      break room and storage

      for all clues!'
    mood: 0
  - text: Collect all fragments, solve the terminal puzzle, get the keycard and reach
      the elevator!
    mood: 3
  - text: "REMEMBER CONTROLS:\nMove \u2192 Left Joystick \nLook \u2192 Right Joystick\nInteract
      \u2192 Tap the screen"
    mood: 3
  - text: Good luck Gamer! The database is counting on you!
    mood: 1
